{ Needless to say, we preserve the bishop and will now aim to get in f2-f4, a2-a3 and Bd3. It's also worth pointing out that Black should now continue with  10...Bb7  as ...Ba6 ideas blunder a piece to c2-c3, since the knight on b4 then lacks a safe square. }
