{ Bagging a pawn and as played by Uzbek Olympiad gold medallist, Jahongir Vakhidov @@StartBracket@@if you really like your bishops then by all means prefer  13.dxe5  dxe4  14.Bc4  ,  with an edge as we saw via an  @@StartFEN@@2rq1rk1/pb2bppp/1pn1pn2/2ppN3/3P1P2/PP1BP3/1BPN2PP/R2Q1RK1 b - - 0 11@@EndFEN@@  11...Nxe5  12.dxe5  Ne4  move order@@EndBracket@@. }
