{ Steady away and completing development with tempo. There's no rush to go Rf3-h3 and, indeed,  12.Rf3  can be met well enough by  12...Nxe5  13.fxe5  Ne4  . }
12... b5 13. dxc5
{ The simplest way of dealing with the threat of ...c4, opening up the long diagonal for the Zukertort bishop in the process. }
