14... Ng6 15. c3
{ A new engine-approved idea and more good prophylaxis. White's position looks slightly easier to play. We're intending to meet ... Qe7 with Ra1 and only then a3-a4, seizing some space while avoiding any ...Bxa3 issues. On the kingside, one way to increase the pressure is Rf3, Qe3 and Rh3, with g2-g3 followed by h2-h4-h5 another possibility. }
