14... Nc5 15. Bxh7+ Kxh7 16. Ng5+
{ There may not be a bishop on the c1-h6 diagonal, but the Greek Gift is still extremely strong here, and if  16...Kg6?  17.Qg4  Nxe5  18.Bxe5  Qxe5  19.Nf3+   or  16...Kh6?  17.Qe3  .  As such, the king pretty much must retreat: }
16... Kg8 17. Qh5 Rfe8 18. f4
{ Simple chess. Rather than drive the king towards safety, White introduces another attacker @@StartBracket@@the rook on f1@@EndBracket@@. The engines feel that White is already close to winning with f4-f5 being such a large threat. }
