15... d4 16. Nf1 dxe3 17. Nxe3
{ Suddenly Bxh7+ is an issue and  17...Qe7?  @@StartBracket@@to keep the knight on f6 secure@@EndBracket@@ pretty much loses to  18.Nf5  . }
