13... Qd7 14. Rfd1
{ This was very solid for Black in Gledura-Bok, Internet @@StartBracket@@rapid@@EndBracket@@ 2021, but at least White had the ideas of both Nd2-f3-e5 and Nd4-f3 followed by e3-e4, Ne5 or Ng5. }
