6. g4 { Springing the trap shut as White seizes the initiative. } 6... Bg6 7.
Ne5
{ A key follow-up as White threatens to cause mayhem on the kingside with @@StartFEN@@rn1qkb1r/ppp2ppp/4pnb1/3pN3/3P2P1/4P2P/PPPN1P2/R1BQKB1R w KQkq - 0 7@@EndFEN@@  8.h4  and if  8...h6  simply  9.Nxg6  fxg6  10.Bd3  . }
