{ Supporting e2-e4 to take over the centre, although the gambit  5.e4!?  is also extremely tempting - and strong. }
5... Nf6 6. f3
{ White is about to obtain an ideal centre while regaining his pawn on c4 and leaving Black looking a little cramped. }
