7... Nf6 8. Nc3
{ White prepares to increase the pressure on d5 with Bg5 and has also spotted that  8...d4?  9.Na4!  would cause definite problems for Black. }
8... O-O 9. Bg5 Bg4 10. h3 Be6 11. Qd3
