12... d5 13. Rac1
{ Black was very solid here in Petkevich-Danielsen, Lyngby 1990, but White should not be unhappy.   We should be on the lookout for a timely c4-c5 and may also consider b4!? dxc4; Nxc4, taking on an IQP in return for getting in b4-b5 and Nce5, looking to seize the initiative. }
