{ The dynamic and best recapture, putting the d4-d5 advance firmly back on the agenda. The c4- and d4-pawn duo are also fairly secure, allowing White to manoeuvre, as with Rfe1 and Bb1, looking to set up a battery against h7 with Qd3. }
