[SetUp "1"]

11... Qxc2
{ In this variation with an early ...Nb4, if Black gets too greedy against c2, how can we punish them? }
12. Qxc2 Nxc2 13. Ra2
{ Just as when the bishop was on e7, we find that the knight is trapped and will be forced to give itself up for just two pawns after Bd3 and/or Rc1. }
13... Bd7 14. Rc1 Rac8 15. Bd3 { And the knight is finally trapped. } *

