15... Rf7
{ Black's forces are scattered and it sometimes doesn't take much for White to break through. }
16. Bxh7+ { A typical deflection. } 16... Kf8 { 16...Kxh7  17.Qxf7 } 17. Bg6
{ White is winning a rook - Black can resign. } 17... Re7 18. Qh3
{ And to give you an idea how hopeless this is, Black's only way not to be mated immediately is ...Rf7 back. }
