[SetUp "1"]

13... Nxe5
{ Here our bishops AND the f-file are open. This is a good indicator there should be tactics lurking. }
14. Rxf6 { Once again, removing this key defender is quick to herald the end: }
14... gxf6 15. Qh5
{ Black is completely lost with Qh6 a serious inconvenience, as well as, of course, mate on h7, and taking on d3 only stumbles into a different mate: }
15... Nxd3 { 15...f5  does not help after  16.Qg5+  Ng6  17.Bf6 } 16. Qg4+ Kh8
17. Bxf6# *

