[SetUp "1"]

Ba6
{ Black's clever maneuver to attempt to exchange the bishops falls short. How do we punish it? }
11. c3
{ Black forgot that after the queen recaptures on e2, the knight will be trapped! }
11... Bxe2 12. Qxe2 Nc2 13. Rac1 { There goes the knight. } *

[Event "?"]
[Site "?"]
[Date "????.??.??"]
[Round "?"]
[White "Thematic Tactics"]
[Black "Thematic Tactic #15 "]
[Result "*"]
