[SetUp "1"]

18... f6
{ Susan Polgar has just forced her opponent to block the diagonal with ...f6. How did she end the game? }
19. Qxe6+ { Breaking through and preparing a further rook invasion. } 19... Kh8
20. Rd7 { A decisive invasion. } 20... Rc6 21. Qg4
{ Black has no defense to the threats on the light-squared bishop and the g7 square.   Polgar, Susan vs. Thi Thanh Huong Mai, 1990 Women's Olympiad }
*

[Event "?"]
[Site "?"]
[Date "????.??.??"]
[Round "?"]
[White "Thematic Tactics"]
[Black "Thematic Tactic #17 "]
[Result "*"]
